name: Monthly Habit Tracker Template
description:
Been getting a lot of joy out of bullet journaling lately. Got curious about how to bring the practice of analog habit-tracking into a digital format while carrying over the simplicity and visual nature. Still experimenting with the idea but thought I'd share for anyone who's also interested!

Shoutout to @tomreinert for the original calendar components! I simply worked on formatting it into a monthly template.
